<HEADLINE> Finland Wins World Cup Qualifier over Albania </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HELSINKI, September 2 (Xinhua) -- Finland overcame a 10-man
disadvantage for the last 20 minutes to beat Albania 2-1 in their
opening Group Nine World Cup qualifying match on Saturday.
</P>
