</P>
<P>
-- U.S. President Bill Clinton announced that he will not
authorize deployment of a national missile defense system but will
leave the final decision to his successor because the technical
uncertainties and diplomatic costs are too great at this time.
</P>
<P>
-- An appeal court in Denver acted on its own accord and
