Council comprising eight chief executive officers and chairmen of
U.S. multinational companies specializing in hi-tech environment
on an eight-day trade mission to Malaysia.
</P>
<P>
Malaysia is the largest source of imports among the ASEAN
countries and ranks 11th globally as a source of U.S. imports.
</P>
<P>
