<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, September 1 (Xinhua) -- The United States women's
soccer team whitewashed their Brazilian counterparts 4-0 in the
warm-up game in San Jose of California. just 15 days before the
Sydney Olympic Games.
</P>
<P>
