dating to 1997, including the semifinal on the way to the 1999
World Cup title.
</P>
<P>
Their first game will be September 14 against Norway, which
handed the U.S. team three of its four defeats in 2000. Three days
later, the United States will face World Cup runner-up China in a
repeat of the 1999 World Cup final which was decided by penalties
shootings. 
